	<p>
    <p><a href="http://www.stationaryisbad.com/">Stationery is bad</a>.&nbsp; I suspect that Scoble won&rsquo;t have any problem&nbsp;giving some of his link-juice to&nbsp;this site.&nbsp; I felt a mild ickiness at having to drop my firewall&rsquo;s default rejection of MIME-type integrated objects&mdash;something I often have to do&mdash;but I laughed so hard I almost hurt myself.&nbsp; &nbsp;To grasp all of the physical comedy, I had to watch each video 4 times, and I still may have missed something.</p><p>Thanks to <a href="http://www.pringle.net.nz/blog/PermaLink,guid,05a8eb90-955c-4ce0-b5e1-414b1c12bac2.aspx">Craig Pringle</a>&nbsp;and a parade of other&nbsp;TabletPC advocates who now not only feel cool but supported as well.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><em></em></p>
